Class Contact

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ru.reksoft.contacts.Contact
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Contact>

    public class Contact
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Contact>, java.io.Serializable
    Simply class, that storage information about person that includes:
    name (could be first name with last name, or only first name, or just nickname - no difference);
    list of phone numbers (without naming ones);
    and additional information with any data also could stored;
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
